           <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/1328810ae8a318cb3946ba3f2e931589.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides fade\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext\">15 / 20</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/73e2c377be7660cd20d49cc1c045201f.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n    \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides fade\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext\">16 / 20</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/06c4de02ae4a6de31dc522059edddfc1.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides fade\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext\">17 / 20</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/55c98a29aa4be4e6b8670987cc8d18d0.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides fade\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext\">18 / 20</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/505953a527ea157280b64357ca933d87.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n    \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides fade\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext\">19 / 20</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/4a44401cd1634026448da33773b4c963.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides fade\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext\">20 / 20</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position\" src=\"/64680da468c915b23424fa556236d97e.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n    \r\n            <a class=\"prev\" onclick=\"plusSlides(-1)\">&#10094;</a>\r\n            <a class=\"next\" onclick=\"plusSlides(1)\">&#10095;</a>\r\n            \r\n        </div>\r\n            \r\n        <br>\r\n            \r\n        <div style=\"text-align:center\">\r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(1)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(2)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(3)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(4)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(5)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(6)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(7)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(8)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(9)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(10)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(11)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(12)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(13)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(14)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(15)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(16)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(17)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(18)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(19)\"></span> \r\n            <span class=\"dot\" onclick=\"currentSlide(20)\"></span> \r\n        </div>\r\n    \r\n        <div class=\"paragraph-container\">\r\n            <p>\r\n                Project JunkRace, the initial idea was to create a mobile game that was a karting game with steam-punk, \r\n                post-apocalyptic elements presented throughout. To make the experience a lot more different from other karting \r\n                games was the apply cool-downs and character specific vehicles to the game. The inspirations for the game took \r\n                elements from other games such as Mario kart, Overwatch and League of Legends.  \r\n            </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Each character would also have their own specific abilities on a cool-down timer, which would have to be \r\n                thoroughly tested to see which can be over-used and over-powered. \r\n            </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                There were plans to either make characters have character specific cool-downs or just cool-down abilities that every \r\n                character can use. We already thought to restrict the abilities to 2 cool-downs and 1 Ultimate ability.  Even though \r\n                the initial idea of cool-downs was interesting, it was decided that with the character specific cool-downs it would only \r\n                be limited to 2 cool-downs per character without having the need to change them so they would be fixed and easier to understand.  \r\n            </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                In addition, the idea was to have at least 6 different characters that have different vehicles/play-styles, with the decision \r\n                of splitting the characters into two separate but easy to understand classes; one class being light and the other being heavy \r\n                vehicles. \r\n            </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                For the beginning or the prototype stage, two stages were created for the racers. One was a moving spider stage whilst the other was \r\n                a simple canyon looking arena. Both of these stages had their own secrets to uncover to make them more interesting for the \r\n                player, mostly they had just shortcuts to allow for diverse play. \r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <br>\r\n\r\n        <h2 class=\"sub-title\"> Project Diamonds </h2>\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"slideshow-container2\">\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"image-slides2 fade2\">\r\n                <div class=\"numbertext2\">1 / 23</div>\r\n                <img class=\"image-position2\" src=\"/879180a3bb93f9073d79de38bc343c48.png\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"image-slides2 fade2\">\r\n                <div clas